+    `times', `mtimes', `and', and `or') have been extended to accept
+    multiple arguments.  This is especially useful for summing
+    (multiplying, etc.) lists of objects (of possibly distinct types):
+   
+      matrix_sum = plus (matrix_list{:});
+
